{"surah":{"number":70,"name":"المعارج","englishName":"Al-Ma'arij","englishTranslation":"The Ascending Stairways","ayahCount":44},"sources":["Quran.com API v4 (word-by-word Uthmani + English glosses + word audio)","AlQuran.cloud / Tanzil quran-uthmani (independent text verification)","AlQuran.cloud / Saheeh International (flowing English translation)","Quranic Arabic Corpus morphology (word roots)"],"generatedAt":"2026-07-03T04:01:31.180Z","ayahs":[{"number":1,"translation":"A supplicant asked for a punishment bound to happen","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"سَأَلَ","english":"Asked","translit":"sa-ala","root":"سأل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"سَآئِلٌۢ","english":"a questioner","translit":"sāilun","root":"سأل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"بِعَذَابٍۢ","english":"about a punishment","translit":"biʿadhābin","root":"عذب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَاقِعٍۢ","english":"bound to happen","translit":"wāqiʿin","root":"وقع"}]},{"number":2,"translation":"To the disbelievers; of it there is no preventer.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"لِّلْكَـٰفِرِينَ","english":"To the disbelievers","translit":"lil'kāfirīna","root":"كفر"},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَيْسَ","english":"not","translit":"laysa","root":"ليس"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لَهُۥ","english":"of it","translit":"lahu","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"دَافِعٌۭ","english":"any preventer","translit":"dāfiʿun","root":"دفع"}]},{"number":3,"translation":"[It is] from Allah, owner of the ways of ascent.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"مِّنَ","english":"From","translit":"mina","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-lahi","root":"أله"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ذِى","english":"Owner","translit":"dhī","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْمَعَارِجِ","english":"(of) the ways of ascent","translit":"l-maʿāriji","root":"عرج"}]},{"number":4,"translation":"The angels and the Spirit will ascend to Him during a Day the extent of which is fifty thousand years.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"تَعْرُجُ","english":"Ascend","translit":"taʿruju","root":"عرج"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْمَلَـٰٓئِكَةُ","english":"the Angels","translit":"l-malāikatu","root":"ملك"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَٱلرُّوحُ","english":"and the Spirit","translit":"wal-rūḥu","root":"روح"},{"position":4,"arabic":"إِلَيْهِ","english":"to Him","translit":"ilayhi","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"فِى","english":"in","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"يَوْمٍۢ","english":"a Day","translit":"yawmin","root":"يوم"},{"position":7,"arabic":"كَانَ","english":"[is]","translit":"kāna","root":"كون"},{"position":8,"arabic":"مِقْدَارُهُۥ","english":"its measure","translit":"miq'dāruhu","root":"قدر"},{"position":9,"arabic":"خَمْسِينَ","english":"(is) fifty","translit":"khamsīna","root":"خمس"},{"position":10,"arabic":"أَلْفَ","english":"thousand","translit":"alfa","root":"ألف"},{"position":11,"arabic":"سَنَةٍۢ","english":"year(s)","translit":"sanatin","root":"سنو"}]},{"number":5,"translation":"So be patient with gracious patience.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَٱصْبِرْ","english":"So be patient","translit":"fa-iṣ'bir","root":"صبر"},{"position":2,"arabic":"صَبْرًۭا","english":"a patience","translit":"ṣabran","root":"صبر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"جَمِيلًا","english":"good","translit":"jamīlan","root":"جمل"}]},{"number":6,"translation":"Indeed, they see it [as] distant,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّهُمْ","english":"Indeed, they","translit":"innahum","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَرَوْنَهُۥ","english":"see it","translit":"yarawnahu","root":"رأي"},{"position":3,"arabic":"بَعِيدًۭا","english":"(as) far off","translit":"baʿīdan","root":"بعد"}]},{"number":7,"translation":"But We see it [as] near.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَنَرَىٰهُ","english":"But We see it","translit":"wanarāhu","root":"رأي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"قَرِيبًۭا","english":"near","translit":"qarīban","root":"قرب"}]},{"number":8,"translation":"On the Day the sky will be like murky oil,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَوْمَ","english":"(The) Day","translit":"yawma","root":"يوم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"تَكُونُ","english":"will be","translit":"takūnu","root":"كون"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَآءُ","english":"the sky","translit":"l-samāu","root":"سمو"},{"position":4,"arabic":"كَٱلْمُهْلِ","english":"like molten copper","translit":"kal-muh'li","root":"مهل"}]},{"number":9,"translation":"And the mountains will be like wool,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَتَكُونُ","english":"And will be","translit":"watakūnu","root":"كون"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْجِبَالُ","english":"the mountains","translit":"l-jibālu","root":"جبل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"كَٱلْعِهْنِ","english":"like wool","translit":"kal-ʿih'ni","root":"عهن"}]},{"number":10,"translation":"And no friend will ask [anything of] a friend,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَا","english":"And not","translit":"walā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَسْـَٔلُ","english":"will ask","translit":"yasalu","root":"سأل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"حَمِيمٌ","english":"a friend","translit":"ḥamīmun","root":"حمم"},{"position":4,"arabic":"حَمِيمًۭا","english":"(about) a friend","translit":"ḥamīman","root":"حمم"}]},{"number":11,"translation":"They will be shown each other. The criminal will wish that he could be ransomed from the punishment of that Day by his children","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يُبَصَّرُونَهُمْ ۚ","english":"They will be made to see each other","translit":"yubaṣṣarūnahum","root":"بصر"},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَوَدُّ","english":"Would wish","translit":"yawaddu","root":"ودد","audio":"wbw/070_011_003.mp3"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْمُجْرِمُ","english":"the criminal","translit":"l-muj'rimu","root":"جرم","audio":"wbw/070_011_004.mp3"},{"position":4,"arabic":"لَوْ","english":"if","translit":"law","root":"","audio":"wbw/070_011_005.mp3"},{"position":5,"arabic":"يَفْتَدِى","english":"he (could be) ransomed","translit":"yaftadī","root":"فدي","audio":"wbw/070_011_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"مِنْ","english":"from","translit":"min","root":"","audio":"wbw/070_011_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"عَذَابِ","english":"(the) punishment","translit":"ʿadhābi","root":"عذب","audio":"wbw/070_011_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"يَوْمِئِذٍۭ","english":"(of) that Day","translit":"yawmi-idhin","root":"يوم","audio":"wbw/070_011_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"بِبَنِيهِ","english":"by his children","translit":"bibanīhi","root":"بني","audio":"wbw/070_011_010.mp3"}]},{"number":12,"translation":"And his wife and his brother","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَصَـٰحِبَتِهِۦ","english":"And his spouse","translit":"waṣāḥibatihi","root":"صحب"},{"position":2,"arabic":"وَأَخِيهِ","english":"and his brother","translit":"wa-akhīhi","root":"أخو"}]},{"number":13,"translation":"And his nearest kindred who shelter him","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَفَصِيلَتِهِ","english":"And his nearest kindred","translit":"wafaṣīlatihi","root":"فصل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّتِى","english":"who","translit":"allatī","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"تُـْٔوِيهِ","english":"sheltered him","translit":"tu'wīhi","root":"أوي"}]},{"number":14,"translation":"And whoever is on earth entirely [so] then it could save him.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَن","english":"And whoever","translit":"waman","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"فِى","english":"(is) on","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرْضِ","english":"the earth","translit":"l-arḍi","root":"أرض"},{"position":4,"arabic":"جَمِيعًۭا","english":"all","translit":"jamīʿan","root":"جمع"},{"position":5,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","english":"then","translit":"thumma","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"يُنجِيهِ","english":"it (could) save him","translit":"yunjīhi","root":"نجو"}]},{"number":15,"translation":"No! Indeed, it is the Flame [of Hell],","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"كَلَّآ ۖ","english":"By no means","translit":"kallā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"إِنَّهَا","english":"Indeed, it (is)","translit":"innahā","root":"","audio":"wbw/070_015_003.mp3"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لَظَىٰ","english":"surely a Flame of Hell","translit":"laẓā","root":"","audio":"wbw/070_015_004.mp3"}]},{"number":16,"translation":"A remover of exteriors.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"نَزَّاعَةًۭ","english":"A remover","translit":"nazzāʿatan","root":"نزع"},{"position":2,"arabic":"لِّلشَّوَىٰ","english":"of the skin of the head","translit":"lilshawā","root":"شوي"}]},{"number":17,"translation":"It invites he who turned his back [on truth] and went away [from obedience]","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"تَدْعُوا۟","english":"Inviting","translit":"tadʿū","root":"دعو"},{"position":2,"arabic":"مَنْ","english":"(him) who","translit":"man","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"أَدْبَرَ","english":"turned his back","translit":"adbara","root":"دبر"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَتَوَلَّىٰ","english":"and went away","translit":"watawallā","root":"ولي"}]},{"number":18,"translation":"And collected [wealth] and hoarded.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَجَمَعَ","english":"And collected","translit":"wajamaʿa","root":"جمع"},{"position":2,"arabic":"فَأَوْعَىٰٓ","english":"and hoarded","translit":"fa-awʿā","root":"وعي"}]},{"number":19,"translation":"Indeed, mankind was created anxious:","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"۞ إِنَّ","english":"Indeed","translit":"inna","root":"","audio":"wbw/070_019_002.mp3"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْإِنسَـٰنَ","english":"the man","translit":"l-insāna","root":"أنس","audio":"wbw/070_019_003.mp3"},{"position":3,"arabic":"خُلِقَ","english":"was created","translit":"khuliqa","root":"خلق","audio":"wbw/070_019_004.mp3"},{"position":4,"arabic":"هَلُوعًا","english":"anxious","translit":"halūʿan","root":"هلع","audio":"wbw/070_019_005.mp3"}]},{"number":20,"translation":"When evil touches him, impatient,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِذَا","english":"When","translit":"idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"مَسَّهُ","english":"touches him","translit":"massahu","root":"مسس"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلشَّرُّ","english":"the evil","translit":"l-sharu","root":"شرر"},{"position":4,"arabic":"جَزُوعًۭا","english":"distressed","translit":"jazūʿan","root":"جزع"}]},{"number":21,"translation":"And when good touches him, withholding [of it],","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذَا","english":"And when","translit":"wa-idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"مَسَّهُ","english":"touches him","translit":"massahu","root":"مسس"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْخَيْرُ","english":"the good","translit":"l-khayru","root":"خير"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مَنُوعًا","english":"withholding","translit":"manūʿan","root":"منع"}]},{"number":22,"translation":"Except the observers of prayer -","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِلَّا","english":"Except","translit":"illā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْمُصَلِّينَ","english":"those who pray","translit":"l-muṣalīna","root":"صلو"}]},{"number":23,"translation":"Those who are constant in their prayer","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","english":"Those who","translit":"alladhīna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"هُمْ","english":"[they]","translit":"hum","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","english":"at","translit":"ʿalā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"صَلَاتِهِمْ","english":"their prayer","translit":"ṣalātihim","root":"صلو"},{"position":5,"arabic":"دَآئِمُونَ","english":"(are) constant","translit":"dāimūna","root":"دوم"}]},{"number":24,"translation":"And those within whose wealth is a known right","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ","english":"And those who","translit":"wa-alladhīna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"فِىٓ","english":"in","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"أَمْوَٰلِهِمْ","english":"their wealth","translit":"amwālihim","root":"مول"},{"position":4,"arabic":"حَقٌّۭ","english":"(is) a right","translit":"ḥaqqun","root":"حقق"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مَّعْلُومٌۭ","english":"known","translit":"maʿlūmun","root":"علم"}]},{"number":25,"translation":"For the petitioner and the deprived -","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"لِّلسَّآئِلِ","english":"For the one who asks","translit":"lilssāili","root":"سأل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"وَٱلْمَحْرُومِ","english":"and the deprived","translit":"wal-maḥrūmi","root":"حرم"}]},{"number":26,"translation":"And those who believe in the Day of Recompense","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ","english":"And those who","translit":"wa-alladhīna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يُصَدِّقُونَ","english":"accept (the) truth","translit":"yuṣaddiqūna","root":"صدق"},{"position":3,"arabic":"بِيَوْمِ","english":"(of the) Day","translit":"biyawmi","root":"يوم"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلدِّينِ","english":"(of) the Judgment","translit":"l-dīni","root":"دين"}]},{"number":27,"translation":"And those who are fearful of the punishment of their Lord -","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ","english":"And those who","translit":"wa-alladhīna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"هُم","english":"[they]","translit":"hum","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"مِّنْ","english":"of","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"عَذَابِ","english":"(the) punishment","translit":"ʿadhābi","root":"عذب"},{"position":5,"arabic":"رَبِّهِم","english":"(of) their Lord","translit":"rabbihim","root":"ربب"},{"position":6,"arabic":"مُّشْفِقُونَ","english":"(are) fearful","translit":"mush'fiqūna","root":"شفق"}]},{"number":28,"translation":"Indeed, the punishment of their Lord is not that from which one is safe -","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّ","english":"Indeed","translit":"inna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"عَذَابَ","english":"(the) punishment","translit":"ʿadhāba","root":"عذب"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبِّهِمْ","english":"(of) your Lord","translit":"rabbihim","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"غَيْرُ","english":"(is) not","translit":"ghayru","root":"غير"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مَأْمُونٍۢ","english":"to be felt secure (of)","translit":"mamūnin","root":"أمن"}]},{"number":29,"translation":"And those who guard their private parts","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ","english":"And those who","translit":"wa-alladhīna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"هُمْ","english":"[they]","translit":"hum","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"لِفُرُوجِهِمْ","english":"their modesty","translit":"lifurūjihim","root":"فرج"},{"position":4,"arabic":"حَـٰفِظُونَ","english":"(are) guardians","translit":"ḥāfiẓūna","root":"حفظ"}]},{"number":30,"translation":"Except from their wives or those their right hands possess, for indeed, they are not to be blamed -","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِلَّا","english":"Except","translit":"illā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"عَلَىٰٓ","english":"from","translit":"ʿalā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"أَزْوَٰجِهِمْ","english":"their spouses","translit":"azwājihim","root":"زوج"},{"position":4,"arabic":"أَوْ","english":"or","translit":"aw","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"مَا","english":"what","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"مَلَكَتْ","english":"they possess","translit":"malakat","root":"ملك"},{"position":7,"arabic":"أَيْمَـٰنُهُمْ","english":"rightfully","translit":"aymānuhum","root":"يمن"},{"position":8,"arabic":"فَإِنَّهُمْ","english":"then indeed, they","translit":"fa-innahum","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"غَيْرُ","english":"(are) not","translit":"ghayru","root":"غير"},{"position":10,"arabic":"مَلُومِينَ","english":"blameworthy","translit":"malūmīna","root":"لوم"}]},{"number":31,"translation":"But whoever seeks beyond that, then they are the transgressors -","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَمَنِ","english":"But whoever","translit":"famani","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱبْتَغَىٰ","english":"seeks","translit":"ib'taghā","root":"بغي"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَرَآءَ","english":"beyond","translit":"warāa","root":"وري"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","english":"that","translit":"dhālika","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"فَأُو۟لَـٰٓئِكَ","english":"then those","translit":"fa-ulāika","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"هُمُ","english":"[they]","translit":"humu","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلْعَادُونَ","english":"(are) the transgressors","translit":"l-ʿādūna","root":"عدو"}]},{"number":32,"translation":"And those who are to their trusts and promises attentive","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ","english":"And those who","translit":"wa-alladhīna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"هُمْ","english":"[they]","translit":"hum","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"لِأَمَـٰنَـٰتِهِمْ","english":"of their trusts","translit":"li-amānātihim","root":"أمن"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَعَهْدِهِمْ","english":"and their promise","translit":"waʿahdihim","root":"عهد"},{"position":5,"arabic":"رَٰعُونَ","english":"(are) observers","translit":"rāʿūna","root":"رعي"}]},{"number":33,"translation":"And those who are in their testimonies upright","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ","english":"And those who","translit":"wa-alladhīna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"هُم","english":"[they]","translit":"hum","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"بِشَهَـٰدَٰتِهِمْ","english":"in their testimonies","translit":"bishahādātihim","root":"شهد"},{"position":4,"arabic":"قَآئِمُونَ","english":"stand firm","translit":"qāimūna","root":"قوم"}]},{"number":34,"translation":"And those who [carefully] maintain their prayer:","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ","english":"And those who","translit":"wa-alladhīna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"هُمْ","english":"[they]","translit":"hum","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","english":"on","translit":"ʿalā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"صَلَاتِهِمْ","english":"their prayer","translit":"ṣalātihim","root":"صلو"},{"position":5,"arabic":"يُحَافِظُونَ","english":"keep a guard","translit":"yuḥāfiẓūna","root":"حفظ"}]},{"number":35,"translation":"They will be in gardens, honored.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"أُو۟لَـٰٓئِكَ","english":"Those","translit":"ulāika","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"فِى","english":"(will be) in","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"جَنَّـٰتٍۢ","english":"Gardens","translit":"jannātin","root":"جنن"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مُّكْرَمُونَ","english":"honored","translit":"muk'ramūna","root":"كرم"}]},{"number":36,"translation":"So what is [the matter] with those who disbelieve, hastening [from] before you, [O Muhammad],","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَمَالِ","english":"So what is with","translit":"famāli","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","english":"those who","translit":"alladhīna","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"كَفَرُوا۟","english":"disbelieve","translit":"kafarū","root":"كفر"},{"position":4,"arabic":"قِبَلَكَ","english":"before you","translit":"qibalaka","root":"قبل"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مُهْطِعِينَ","english":"(they) hasten","translit":"muh'ṭiʿīna","root":"هطع"}]},{"number":37,"translation":"[To sit] on [your] right and [your] left in separate groups?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"عَنِ","english":"On","translit":"ʿani","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْيَمِينِ","english":"the right","translit":"l-yamīni","root":"يمن"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَعَنِ","english":"and on","translit":"waʿani","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلشِّمَالِ","english":"the left","translit":"l-shimāli","root":"شمل"},{"position":5,"arabic":"عِزِينَ","english":"(in) separate groups","translit":"ʿizīna","root":"عزو"}]},{"number":38,"translation":"Does every person among them aspire to enter a garden of pleasure?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"أَيَطْمَعُ","english":"Does long","translit":"ayaṭmaʿu","root":"طمع"},{"position":2,"arabic":"كُلُّ","english":"every","translit":"kullu","root":"كلل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱمْرِئٍۢ","english":"person","translit":"im'ri-in","root":"مرأ"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مِّنْهُمْ","english":"among them","translit":"min'hum","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"أَن","english":"that","translit":"an","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"يُدْخَلَ","english":"he enters","translit":"yud'khala","root":"دخل"},{"position":7,"arabic":"جَنَّةَ","english":"a Garden","translit":"jannata","root":"جنن"},{"position":8,"arabic":"نَعِيمٍۢ","english":"(of) Delight","translit":"naʿīmin","root":"نعم"}]},{"number":39,"translation":"No! Indeed, We have created them from that which they know.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"كَلَّآ ۖ","english":"By no means","translit":"kallā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"إِنَّا","english":"Indeed, We","translit":"innā","root":"","audio":"wbw/070_039_003.mp3"},{"position":3,"arabic":"خَلَقْنَـٰهُم","english":"[We] have created them","translit":"khalaqnāhum","root":"خلق","audio":"wbw/070_039_004.mp3"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مِّمَّا","english":"from what","translit":"mimmā","root":"","audio":"wbw/070_039_005.mp3"},{"position":5,"arabic":"يَعْلَمُونَ","english":"they know","translit":"yaʿlamūna","root":"علم","audio":"wbw/070_039_006.mp3"}]},{"number":40,"translation":"So I swear by the Lord of [all] risings and settings that indeed We are able","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَلَآ","english":"But nay","translit":"falā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أُقْسِمُ","english":"I swear","translit":"uq'simu","root":"قسم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"بِرَبِّ","english":"by (the) Lord","translit":"birabbi","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْمَشَـٰرِقِ","english":"(of) the risings","translit":"l-mashāriqi","root":"شرق"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَٱلْمَغَـٰرِبِ","english":"and the settings","translit":"wal-maghāribi","root":"غرب"},{"position":6,"arabic":"إِنَّا","english":"that We","translit":"innā","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"لَقَـٰدِرُونَ","english":"(are) surely Able","translit":"laqādirūna","root":"قدر"}]},{"number":41,"translation":"To replace them with better than them; and We are not to be outdone.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"عَلَىٰٓ","english":"[On]","translit":"ʿalā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَن","english":"to","translit":"an","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"نُّبَدِّلَ","english":"[We] replace","translit":"nubaddila","root":"بدل"},{"position":4,"arabic":"خَيْرًۭا","english":"(with) better","translit":"khayran","root":"خير"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مِّنْهُمْ","english":"than them","translit":"min'hum","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَمَا","english":"and not","translit":"wamā","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"نَحْنُ","english":"We","translit":"naḥnu","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"بِمَسْبُوقِينَ","english":"(are) to be outrun","translit":"bimasbūqīna","root":"سبق"}]},{"number":42,"translation":"So leave them to converse vainly and amuse themselves until they meet their Day which they are promised -","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَذَرْهُمْ","english":"So leave them","translit":"fadharhum","root":"وذر"},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَخُوضُوا۟","english":"(to) converse vainly","translit":"yakhūḍū","root":"خوض"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَيَلْعَبُوا۟","english":"and amuse themselves","translit":"wayalʿabū","root":"لعب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"حَتَّىٰ","english":"until","translit":"ḥattā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"يُلَـٰقُوا۟","english":"they meet","translit":"yulāqū","root":"لقي"},{"position":6,"arabic":"يَوْمَهُمُ","english":"their Day","translit":"yawmahumu","root":"يوم"},{"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِى","english":"which","translit":"alladhī","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"يُوعَدُونَ","english":"they are promised","translit":"yūʿadūna","root":"وعد"}]},{"number":43,"translation":"The Day they will emerge from the graves rapidly as if they were, toward an erected idol, hastening.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَوْمَ","english":"(The) Day","translit":"yawma","root":"يوم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَخْرُجُونَ","english":"they will come out","translit":"yakhrujūna","root":"خرج"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مِنَ","english":"from","translit":"mina","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْأَجْدَاثِ","english":"the graves","translit":"l-ajdāthi","root":"جدث"},{"position":5,"arabic":"سِرَاعًۭا","english":"rapidly","translit":"sirāʿan","root":"سرع"},{"position":6,"arabic":"كَأَنَّهُمْ","english":"as if they (were)","translit":"ka-annahum","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"إِلَىٰ","english":"to","translit":"ilā","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"نُصُبٍۢ","english":"a goal","translit":"nuṣubin","root":"نصب"},{"position":9,"arabic":"يُوفِضُونَ","english":"hastening","translit":"yūfiḍūna","root":"وفض"}]},{"number":44,"translation":"Their eyes humbled, humiliation will cover them. That is the Day which they had been promised.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"خَـٰشِعَةً","english":"Humbled","translit":"khāshiʿatan","root":"خشع"},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَبْصَـٰرُهُمْ","english":"their eyesights","translit":"abṣāruhum","root":"بصر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"تَرْهَقُهُمْ","english":"will cover them","translit":"tarhaquhum","root":"رهق"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ذِلَّةٌۭ ۚ","english":"humiliation","translit":"dhillatun","root":"ذلل"},{"position":5,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","english":"That","translit":"dhālika","root":"","audio":"wbw/070_044_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلْيَوْمُ","english":"(is) the Day","translit":"l-yawmu","root":"يوم","audio":"wbw/070_044_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِى","english":"which","translit":"alladhī","root":"","audio":"wbw/070_044_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"كَانُوا۟","english":"they were","translit":"kānū","root":"كون","audio":"wbw/070_044_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"يُوعَدُونَ","english":"promised","translit":"yūʿadūna","root":"وعد","audio":"wbw/070_044_010.mp3"}]}]}
